description: Lists runs of the specified Device Advisor test suite. You can list all runs of the test suite, or the runs of a specific version of the test suite. Requires permission to access the ListSuiteRuns action.

nested_items.name: suiteRunsList
nested_items.description: An array of objects that provide summaries of information about the suite runs in the list.

nested_items.name: suiteDefinitionId
nested_items.description: Suite definition ID of the suite run.

nested_items.name: suiteDefinitionVersion
nested_items.description: Suite definition version of the suite run.

nested_items.name: suiteDefinitionName
nested_items.description: Suite definition name of the suite run.

nested_items.name: suiteRunId
nested_items.description: Suite run ID of the suite run.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: when the suite run was created.

nested_items.name: startedAt
nested_items.description: when the suite run was started.

nested_items.name: passed
nested_items.description: Number of test cases that passed in the suite run.

nested_items.name: failed
nested_items.description: Number of test cases that failed in the suite run.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: A token to retrieve the next set of results.
